data.description: **Call about INTEREST RATE BUY DOWN for lower monthly payment** Don't miss this beautiful, move-in ready, 5 bedroom, 3 bath home with loft and one guest bedroom and full bath downstairs! Your new home has awaits you, featuring custom paint and blinds. Kitchen boasts cherry wood cabinets with wine rack, granite counters, stainless steel appliances, double ovens, extended breakfast bar, bright eat-in kitchen, desk & TWO large pantries. This floor plan is perfect for entertaining with a formal dining room, living room and a separate family room. Gorgeous upgraded stairway leads to large loft and the bedrooms. Master suite has a huge walk-in closet with ample space, dual sinks, separate soaking tub & shower. You will love the oasis in your own backyard complete with crystal clear pool, ramada, extended patio, built in BBQ- and plenty of grass area.  Great location with short distance to all schools in the community, elementary, middle school and high school, plus around the corner from Copper Sky Regional Park.  This park offers, swimming, a variety of sports fields, play areas, skate park, dog park, and frisbee golf course.  You don't want to miss this great opportunity.
